I"_<p>The air that I had felt <br />
The green that I had seen <br />
Reminded me of someone <br />
The fool that I have been</p>

<p>The fool who was alive <br />
Only at his garden <br />
Did he ever step beyond<br />
To find the lofty heaven</p>

<p>The nature and my friends<br />
The table and my door<br />
Humming me a single verse<br />
That I have to travel more</p>

